OL,3,CNew safety signs to be installed amid
OL,4,Cwild water swimming warning
OL,6,FNew signs are to be put up along some
OL,7,Fof Oxfords rivers, lakes and canals
OL,8,Fwarning people about the dangers of
OL,9,Fwild swimming.
OL,11,FSix locations in the city have been
OL,12,Fchosen to feature new signage and
OL,13,Fpublic rescue equipment.
OL,15,FSigns reflecting the different risks
OL,16,Ffrom deep water and strong currents
OL,17,Fwill be positioned at Tumbling Bay,
OL,18,FLongbridges, Hinksey Lake, Fiddlers
OL,19,FIsland, Wolvercote Mill Stream and
OL,20,FSunnymead Park.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
