OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781974080
OL,3,CNew safety signs to be installed amid
OL,4,Cwild water swimming warning
OL,6,FOxford City Council commissioned a
OL,7,Freview and advice from the Royal Life
OL,8,FSaving Society.
OL,10,FThe signs come after the death of 14-
OL,11,Fyear-old Baltazar Da Costa who was
OL,12,Fpulled from the water near to
OL,13,FDonnington Bridge on 27 of May.
OL,15,FAt an inquest into his death, the
OL,16,FCoroner said the cause remains under
OL,17,Finvestigation pending a report from
OL,18,Fthe pathologist.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
