OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781974080
OL,3,CNew safety signs to be installed amid
OL,4,Cwild water swimming warning
OL,6,FThe signs also include a what-three-
OL,7,Fwords location to help direct
OL,8,Femergency services to the correct
OL,9,Flocation in the case of an emergency.
OL,11,FThe signs are expected to be installed
OL,12,Fby the end of June, and Additional
OL,13,FPublic Rescue equipment will be placed
OL,14,Fin some recommended areas.
OL,16,FWild swimming in Oxford's waterways is
OL,17,Fpopular but the council is warning
OL,18,Fabout the risks due to the strength of
OL,19,Fthe current, and risk of cold shock in
OL,20,Fdeep water.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
