FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781974080
OL,3,CNew safety signs to be installed amid
OL,4,Cwild water swimming warning
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "The Council does
OL,7,Fnot encourage wild swimming in
OL,8,FOxford's rivers, lakes, canals, or
OL,9,Fother bodies of water, and those who
OL,10,Fchoose to swim do so at their own risk.
OL,12,F"In Oxford, the safest option for
OL,13,Fswimming is in a pool. Free swimming
OL,14,Fsessions are available at our Council-
OL,15,Fowned leisure centres throughout the
OL,16,Fweek for children and young people
OL,17,Funder 17 who live in Oxford."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
