PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781974080
OL,3,CNew safety signs to be installed amid
OL,4,Cwild water swimming warning
OL,6,FCouncillor Anna Railton, Deputy
OL,7,FLeader, and Cabinet Member for
OL,8,FPlanning and Zero Carbon Oxford said:
OL,9,F"Several injuries and deaths have
OL,10,Foccurred in recent years on Oxford's
OL,11,Fwaterways.
OL,13,F"While Oxford's rivers may look
OL,14,Finviting, especially in hot weather,
OL,15,Fthere are risks from uneven surfaces,
OL,16,Fcold water shock, strong currents and
OL,17,Fsubmerged objects in the water.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
