PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781974080
OL,3,CNew safety signs to be installed amid
OL,4,Cwild water swimming warning
OL,6,F"I hope that the installation of these
OL,7,Fnew signs will help people to
OL,8,Funderstand the dangers of wild
OL,9,Fswimming in these locations and advice
OL,10,Fon what to do if someone is in danger."
